I'm Gwen Ifill.

00:06.640 --> 00:08.508 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And I'm Judy
Woodruff.

00:08.542 --> 00:11.245 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: We bring you the
"NewsHour" tonight
from the Wells Fargo Center in
Philadelphia,

00:11.278 --> 00:14.414 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
