45:28.492 --> 45:31.896 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
It was an overflowing basket of
goodies for
us to choose from.

45:31.929 --> 45:36.334 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And, in fact, we do a show
that's three acts
