45:55.086 --> 45:58.823 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, we're having to be a little
more careful
a little bit -- and digging a
little deeper,

45:58.856 --> 45:59.790 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
for sure.

45:59.824 --> 46:00.791 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Your show is tough.

46:00.825 --> 46:01.792 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
You use tough language.

46:01.826 --> 46:02.793 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
SAMANTHA BEE: Thank you.

46:02.827 --> 46:03.861 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Yes.

46:03.894 --> 46:04.862 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: We could not really
air it here.

46:04.895 --> 46:05.863 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
SAMANTHA BEE: I know.

46:05.896 --> 46:06.864 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
I know.

46:06.897 --> 46:08.633 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
It's a salty show.

46:08.666 --> 46:10.635 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: It's a salty show,
which women
are not used to hearing from --
people are

46:10.668 --> 46:11.969 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
not used to hearing from a
woman.

46:12.003 --> 46:13.804 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
SAMANTHA BEE: No, they're not
that used to
it.

46:13.838 --> 46:16.173 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
GWEN IFILL: What kind of
feedback do you get?

46:16.207 --> 46:20.277 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SAMANTHA BEE: I don't -- you
know, I think
I stay out of the feedback loop,
to be perfectly

46:20.311 --> 46:21.278 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
honest with you.

46:21.312 --> 46:23.114 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
GWEN IFILL: Really?

46:23.147 --> 46:24.548 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SAMANTHA BEE: I don't engage
with it too much,
because I know that I'm doing a
show that

46:24.582 --> 46:25.950 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
comes from my heart.

46:25.983 --> 46:30.988 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We're doing a show that comes
from a place
of passion and interest.

46:31.022 --> 46:34.492 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And we use salty language,
because that's
the language we feel like using
to express

46:34.525 --> 46:35.660 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
our thoughts and our concerns.

46:35.693 --> 46:37.828 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And it's really cathartic for
us.

46:37.862 --> 46:40.231 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And I tend to not drop in to the
criticism
of that.

46:40.264 --> 46:42.500 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I tend to just -- I prefer to do
my own thing.

46:42.533 --> 46:47.905 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I prefer to steer my own ship,
and not -- you
know, I think that any time you
try to create

46:47.938 --> 46:53.778 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
comedy or you try to create a
piece of art
by consensus, you -- I mean,
it's impossible

46:53.811 --> 46:55.379 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
to do a quality product.

46:55.413 --> 46:59.817 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And I think -- so, I don't
listen to critics
all that much.

46:59.850 --> 47:00.951 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
I don't read about myself.

47:00.985 --> 47:01.952 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
It's much better.

47:01.986 --> 47:03.020 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
GWEN IFILL: Sounds good.

47:03.054 --> 47:04.021 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
I'm going to try that.

47:04.055 --> 47:05.122 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(CROSSTALK)

47:05.156 --> 47:06.023 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
SAMANTHA BEE: It's actually
paradise, if I
may.

47:06.057 --> 47:07.792 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(LAUGHTER)

47:07.825 --> 47:08.926 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SAMANTHA BEE: You can live in a
bubble in
which you think you're doing a
good job all

47:08.959 --> 47:10.895 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
the time if you don't read what
other people
say.

47:10.928 --> 47:12.730 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(LAUGHTER)

47:12.763 --> 47:15.032 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Samantha Bee, you
have expressed
some views on how few women
there are doing

47:15.066 --> 47:19.537 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
