comedy or any
kind of comedy, having their own
show.

47:19.570 --> 47:21.038 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Why do you think there aren't
more women doing
that?

47:21.072 --> 47:23.207 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
SAMANTHA BEE: I wish that I had
a great answer
for that.

47:23.240 --> 47:25.276 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I wish that I had a funny and
creative answer.

47:25.309 --> 47:28.112 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But the truth is, I just don't
-- I really
don't know.

47:28.145 --> 47:32.717 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I do think that that will
change, and
I certainly hope that it will
change.

47:32.750 --> 47:35.953 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
I would love to have a
sisterhood of late-night
comedy hosts.

47:35.986 --> 47:38.389 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Do you think it
puts more pressure
on you?

47:38.422 --> 47:42.393 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SAMANTHA BEE: It doesn't --
well, as I said,
I stay out of -- I stay out of
that feedback

47:42.426 --> 47:43.394 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
loop.

47:43.427 --> 47:44.395 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
GWEN IFILL: Pressure...

47:44.428 --> 47:46.163 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(CROSSTALK)

47:46.197 --> 47:47.164 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SAMANTHA BEE: So, the pressure
-- I don't
allow that pressure to really
infiltrate.

47:47.198 --> 47:48.332 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I let that conversation be held
by other people.

47:48.365 --> 47:49.333 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(CROSSTALK)

47:49.366 --> 47:50.935 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Let me ask you this.

47:50.968 --> 47:53.370 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Diversity in newsrooms certainly
is a big
issue.

47:53.404 --> 47:58.008 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
What you see on the air is often
-- reflected
the interests of the people who
are deciding

47:58.042 --> 47:59.844 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
