48:03.748 --> 48:05.783 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Do you have more people of color
than we normally
see?

48:05.816 --> 48:06.751 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
SAMANTHA BEE: We do.

48:06.784 --> 48:07.752 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
We do.

48:07.785 --> 48:09.487 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
I believe we do.

48:09.520 --> 48:13.357 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And we certainly made an
absolute effort to
-- we wanted to create a diverse
workplace.

48:13.390 --> 48:18.462 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
That was one of our missions
from the very
start, because the show runner,
Jo Miller,

48:18.496 --> 48:23.701 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
