who, we feel
like we didn't naturally -- we
didn't fall

48:23.734 --> 48:28.472 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
into comedy and comedy writing
in an obvious
way.

48:28.506 --> 48:32.042 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We didn't set -- we didn't begin
our lives
thinking, I'm going to be a
comedy writer

48:32.076 --> 48:33.711 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
one day and I'm going to host my
own show.

48:33.744 --> 48:36.313 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
We both worked on the fringes.

48:36.347 --> 48:37.314 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
We worked in other jobs.

48:37.348 --> 48:39.950 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
We came to it rather late in
life.

48:39.984 --> 48:45.389 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And so we identify with people
who don't have
access to comedy rooms.

48:45.422 --> 48:49.827 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And we wanted to definitely
