day and in every way.

48:57.301 --> 49:00.304 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Well, we will
keep looking
for you here in Philadelphia.

49:00.337 --> 49:01.972 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
SAMANTHA BEE: Thank you.

49:02.006 --> 49:03.040 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Samantha Bee,
