49:05.342 --> 49:06.310 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
SAMANTHA BEE: Oh.

49:06.343 --> 49:07.311 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: We could use that.

49:07.344 --> 49:10.614 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
SAMANTHA BEE: We could all use a
