this.

50:27.725 --> 50:29.093 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
My name is Jim Bourg.

50:29.126 --> 50:32.363 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I'm the editor in charge of
Washington at
Reuters News Pictures.

50:32.396 --> 50:36.300 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Going back to when I started in
political
photography, in presidential
campaign photography,

50:36.333 --> 50:38.502 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
it used to be a lot more
freewheeling.

50:38.535 --> 50:40.170 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
You used to show up for the
events.

50:40.204 --> 50:44.942 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
You used to have a lot more
interaction with
the candidates, yourself
personally.

50:44.975 --> 50:47.945 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
This campaign has been
dramatically different
in this regard.

50:47.978 --> 50:53.317 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Now the two nominees have staffs
and campaigns
that are much more aggressive
about keeping

50:53.350 --> 50:56.487 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
the press at a distance than we
have ever
experienced before.

50:56.520 --> 51:00.591 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
MARK PETERSON, MSNBC
Photography: All these
events are orchestrated, and I
feel like it's

51:00.624 --> 51:06.931 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
the photographer's job to try
and circumvent
that.

51:06.964 --> 51:09.566 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
My name is Mark Peterson.

51:09.600 --> 51:15.940 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And for this campaign cycle, I
have been doing
pictures for MSNBC Photography.

51:15.973 --> 51:21.345 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I started the Political Theater
Project in
2013.

51:21.378 --> 51:28.319 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
With this, you know, I converted
the stuff
to black and white and really
accented the

51:28.352 --> 51:34.058 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
