make things
have more of a dimension to it
and also to

51:34.091 --> 51:36.527 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
highlight the theatrical nature
of it.

51:36.560 --> 51:39.563 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HILARY SWIFT, The New York
Times: Something
that I kind of discovered early
on was that

51:39.596 --> 51:44.635 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
the crowds were almost more
interesting than
the candidates, because the
crowds really

51:44.668 --> 51:46.937 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
