51:46.971 --> 51:48.772 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
My name is Hilary Swift.

51:48.806 --> 51:51.208 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And I'm a freelance photographer
for The New
York Times.

51:51.241 --> 51:56.647 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
This has been the first campaign
and convention
I have ever been a part of or
worked on.

51:56.680 --> 52:01.385 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It's been really surprising to
me in a lot
of ways in getting to see people
from all

52:01.418 --> 52:07.891 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
over the country coming together
and showing
up to support someone, and often
also showing

52:07.925 --> 52:11.161 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
up to not support ideas that
they don't agree
with.

52:11.195 --> 52:15.866 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MELINA MARA: In 2016, we are
needed.

52:15.899 --> 52:22.706 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
A political photojournalist
brings something
that words can't do, brings the
humanity to

52:22.740 --> 52:24.041 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
the coverage.

52:24.074 --> 52:26.276 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And it really is who this person
is.

52:26.310 --> 52:31.782 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And it really does educate the
voter in a
way that they can say, who are
you?

52:31.815 --> 52:33.217 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Can I vote for you?

52:33.250 --> 52:37.588 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: I don't know what
we would
do without these photographers.

52:37.621 --> 52:39.590 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
They're amazing.

52:39.623 --> 52:42.292 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Once again, a
reminder that still
shots sometimes capture more
than moving pictures.

52:42.326 --> 52:44.795 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: For sure, even
though we love
TV.

52:44.828 --> 52:47.097 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And from here in Philadelphia,
that's the
"NewsHour" for now.

52:47.131 --> 52:49.066 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
But stay with us.

52:49.099 --> 52:52.903 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We will be back right here at
